@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xgvumn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (tmp * (1.00 + (v2 + 0.93 * v0 + 0.63)))
    v0 = wp.cos(v1)
    v0 = (0.78 + wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.86)))
    v2 = 0.57
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v0 + 0.13) - v1))
    data[tid] = v0
